        "jsCode": "// Get the raw text output from the previous AI Agent node\n// Assuming the AI's output is stored in the 'output' or 'text' property of the first item\nconst rawText = $json.output || $json.text; \n\n// --- 1. Extract the Subject ---\n// Split the text at \"Subject:\" and take the second part (the content after \"Subject:\")\nlet subjectLine = rawText.split('Subject:')[1]; \n\n// Then, split that content by the newline character ('\\n') and take the first line, then trim whitespace.\nsubjectLine = subjectLine ? subjectLine.split('\\n')[0].trim() : \"Default Application Subject\";\n\n// --- 2. Extract the Body ---\n// Find the index of the first newline character ('\\n'), which separates the subject line from the body.\nconst firstNewlineIndex = rawText.indexOf('\\n'); \n\n// Get all the text starting one character after the first newline.\nlet emailBody = rawText.substring(firstNewlineIndex + 1).trim();\n\n// Create a new item with the separated data\nreturn [{ \n    json: {\n        email_subject: subjectLine,\n        email_body: emailBody\n    } \n}];"
      },
